Text.SourceString: Calm, <NPCName>Gort</> is. Like still water. Turmoil of past, like storm, has passed. Thank you, Hooman, for releasing <NPCName>Gort</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Calm, <NPCName>Gort</> is. Like still water. Turmoil of past, like storm, has passed. Thank you, Hooman, for releasing <NPCName>Gort</>.

Text.SourceString: Owe one, <NPCName>Gort</> does. Big one. Thank you.
Text.LocalizedString: Owe one, <NPCName>Gort</> does. Big one. Thank you.

Text.SourceString: Clouds above, dark and heavy, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.
Text.LocalizedString: Clouds above, dark and heavy, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.

Text.SourceString: Clouds above, dark and heavy, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.
Text.LocalizedString: Clouds above, dark and heavy, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.

Text.SourceString: Clouds above, dark and cold, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.
Text.LocalizedString: Clouds above, dark and cold, like thoughts once in <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind. But now, like the sun, <NPCName>Gort</> finds clarity.

Text.SourceString: The warmth of the sun is like the fire within <NPCName>Gort</>. It needs careful tending, like the unpredictability of weather.
Text.LocalizedString: The warmth of the sun is like the fire within <NPCName>Gort</>. It needs careful tending, like the unpredictability of weather.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind is at peace. Once a roaring flame, now a gentle ember.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Gort</>'s mind is at peace. Once a roaring flame, now a gentle ember.

Text.SourceString: Birds in the sky, they fly free. They teach about freedom.
Text.LocalizedString: Birds in the sky, they fly free. They teach about freedom.

Text.SourceString: Chirping of birds, melody of nature. Reminds <NPCName>Gort</> of magic's harmony.
Text.LocalizedString: Chirping of birds, melody of nature. Reminds <NPCName>Gort</> of magic's harmony.

Text.SourceString: Fire is <NPCName>Gort</>'s gift and once his curse. Now, use it for good, <NPCName>Gort</> must. Like a forge shaping iron, <NPCName>Gort</> shapes himself.
Text.LocalizedString: Fire is <NPCName>Gort</>'s gift and once his curse. Now, use it for good, <NPCName>Gort</> must. Like a forge shaping iron, <NPCName>Gort</> shapes himself.

Text.SourceString: Flame in <NPCName>Gort</>, controlled now. Once wild, now wise. In its warmth, <NPCName>Gort</> finds new purpose.
Text.LocalizedString: Flame in <NPCName>Gort</>, controlled now. Once wild, now wise. In its warmth, <NPCName>Gort</> finds new purpose.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Gort</> once used fire for darkness. Now, light the path for others, <NPCName>Gort</> seeks.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Gort</> once used fire for darkness. Now, light the path for others, <NPCName>Gort</> seeks.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Gort</> learned much. From ashes of the past, new growth emerges. Fire, not only for destruction but for renewal.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Gort</> learned much. From ashes of the past, new growth emerges. Fire, not only for destruction but for renewal.

Text.SourceString: Fire within <NPCName>Gort</>, mighty but gentle. A protector, not destroyer, <NPCName>Gort</> strives to be.
Text.LocalizedString: Fire within <NPCName>Gort</>, mighty but gentle. A protector, not destroyer, <NPCName>Gort</> strives to be.

Text.SourceString: Young ones eager to learn come to <NPCName>Gort</>. Share his wisdom, he does. Teaching fire's secret, responsibly used.
Text.LocalizedString: Young ones eager to learn come to <NPCName>Gort</>. Share his wisdom, he does. Teaching fire's secret, responsibly used.

Text.SourceString: Respect forests and fields, we must.
Text.LocalizedString: Respect forests and fields, we must.

Text.SourceString: Guardians of trees and streams, we must be.
Text.LocalizedString: Guardians of trees and streams, we must be.

Text.SourceString: Gentle the breeze, mighty the storm. Nature's balance always reforms.
Text.LocalizedString: Gentle the breeze, mighty the storm. Nature's balance always reforms.

Text.SourceString: Ah, <PlayerName>$player</>, you approach. Assistance you seek, <NPCName>Gort</> can provide it.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, <PlayerName>$player</>, you approach. Assistance you seek, <NPCName>Gort</> can provide it.

Text.SourceString: Long, your journey has been.
Text.LocalizedString: Long, your journey has been.

Text.SourceString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Your path has many turns.//Share your tales; <NPCName>Gort</> listens.
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Your path has many turns.//Share your tales; <NPCName>Gort</> listens.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, <NPCName>Gort</> sees questions in your eyes.//Perhaps answers lie in the wisdom of fire.
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$Player</>, <NPCName>Gort</> sees questions in your eyes.//Perhaps answers lie in the wisdom of fire.

Text.SourceString: Warm welcome, brave one. In your presence, comfort <NPCName>Gort</> finds.
Text.LocalizedString: Warm welcome, brave one. In your presence, comfort <NPCName>Gort</> finds.

Text.SourceString: Every leaf and stone holds an old story.
Text.LocalizedString: Every leaf and stone holds an old story.

Text.SourceString: Care for the earth as it cares for us. In its soil, we trust.
Text.LocalizedString: Care for the earth as it cares for us. In its soil, we trust.

Text.SourceString: Legends of old, where giants roamed free. In their steps, wisdom we see.
Text.LocalizedString: Legends of old, where giants roamed free. In their steps, wisdom we see.

Text.SourceString: Elders spoke of fire's dual heart. In its glow, our cultural arts start.
Text.LocalizedString: Elders spoke of fire's dual heart. In its glow, our cultural arts start.

Text.SourceString: Ancient stories speak of merfolk beneath waves. Merfolk, creatures of sea's depth. In their tales, unity and harmony, we find.
Text.LocalizedString: Ancient stories speak of merfolk beneath waves. Merfolk, creatures of sea's depth. In their tales, unity and harmony, we find.

Text.SourceString: Legends tell of mermaid song, strong in unity. Their voices together, like a powerful gong.
Text.LocalizedString: Legends tell of mermaid song, strong in unity. Their voices together, like a powerful gong.

Text.SourceString: Merfolk, guardians of sea's secrets. Together, they must protect nature's delicate sonnet.
Text.LocalizedString: Merfolk, guardians of sea's secrets. Together, they must protect nature's delicate sonnet.

Text.SourceString: From the ocean's heart, merfolk teach. Together, farther we reach.
Text.LocalizedString: From the ocean's heart, merfolk teach. Together, farther we reach.

Text.SourceString: Merfolk magic, deep and ancient. A mystery it remains, even to one like <NPCName>Gort</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Merfolk magic, deep and ancient. A mystery it remains, even to one like <NPCName>Gort</>.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</>, <NPCName>Gong</>, <NPCName>Grog</>, and <NPCName>Giu</>, my siblings. Close once we were, before darkness I chased.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</>, <NPCName>Gong</>, <NPCName>Grog</>, and <NPCName>Giu</>, my siblings. Close once we were, before darkness I chased.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Giu</>, my twin, mirror and shadow. While I was gone, a gap did grow.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Giu</>, my twin, mirror and shadow. While I was gone, a gap did grow.

Text.SourceString: In fire's fury, blinded was I. Siblings' love, near it was, but could not see.
Text.LocalizedString: In fire's fury, blinded was I. Siblings' love, near it was, but could not see.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Giu</>, heart of two, shared and split. In my dark journey, our bond I did forget.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Giu</>, heart of two, shared and split. In my dark journey, our bond I did forget.

Text.SourceString: Now seek I, to make amends. Trust broken, not easy to mend.
Text.LocalizedString: Now seek I, to make amends. Trust broken, not easy to mend.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Groo</>, <NPCName>Gong</>, <NPCName>Grog</> – forgive me, I ask. Rebuilding our bond, an enduring task.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Groo</>, <NPCName>Gong</>, <NPCName>Grog</> – forgive me, I ask. Rebuilding our bond, an enduring task.

Text.SourceString: With <NPCName>Giu</>, my twin, reunite I must. In our shared flame, rekindle trust.
Text.LocalizedString: With <NPCName>Giu</>, my twin, reunite I must. In our shared flame, rekindle trust.

Text.SourceString: Plants and flowers, delicate they grow. Tending them, patience we show.
Text.LocalizedString: Plants and flowers, delicate they grow. Tending them, patience we show.

Text.SourceString: Human food, curious in taste. New flavors to try.
Text.LocalizedString: Human food, curious in taste. New flavors to try.

Text.SourceString: Bread and fruits, unlike our fare. Trying them, an experience rare.
Text.LocalizedString: Bread and fruits, unlike our fare. Trying them, an experience rare.

Text.SourceString: Meals shared, bonds grow. Human food, a way to know.
Text.LocalizedString: Meals shared, bonds grow. Human food, a way to know.
